article.headline: Smith's 19 lead Citadel past VMI 76-51
article.description: — AJ Smith scored 19 points and The Citadel beat VMI 76-51 on Saturday.
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — AJ Smith scored 19 points and The Citadel beat VMI 76-51 on Saturday. Smith added nine rebounds for the Bulldogs (10-17, 2-12 Southern Conference). Elijah Morgan scored 15 points and added nine steals. Quentin Millora-Brown had 13 points, while adding 11 rebounds and three blocks. The victory snapped a six-game skid for the Bulldogs. Taeshaud Jackson finished with 13 points, seven rebounds and three steals for the Keydets (4-23, 1-13). Stephen Olowoniyi added 11 points and three blocks for VMI, which has lost eight straight. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
